"windows. Sur windows vous devez utilisez les doubles guillemets (\") à la "
"place."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this context only the <command>sed</command> substitute command is used:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
